<DATELINE>TERRE HAUTE, Ind. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Billy Martin, the brawling former
manager of the New York Yankees, had yet another barroom encounter
when a bullet whizzed past him.
   Martin, who was in town to speak at a fund-raiser for the
Indiana State University baseball team, was sitting at the bar in
Larry Bird's Boston Connection restaurant Saturday when someone
apparently knocked a woman's purse off a chair, setting off her
