<FIRST>r i AM-Bolivia     12-12 0573</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Bolivia,0588</SECOND>
<HEAD>RETRANSMITTING a0723 to fix slugline</HEAD>
<HEAD>Protest Sending Ex-Minister to U.S. for Drug Trial</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Arce Gomez</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By PETER McFARREN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LA PAZ, Bolivia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Supreme Court president and a human
rights group on Tuesday criticized the government for turning over
