Big Board stocks, with Phillips up 1{ to 26 and Exxon up 1\ to 51.
Among other oil issues, Pennzoil gained 1] to 87|, Royal Dutch
Petroleum was up 3{ to 77, Mobil increased 1| to 63, Texaco gained
1 to 56| and Unocal was 1\ higher to 30].
